{
  "stem": "25773.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know what it was, yet I had to go down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They encircled us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- with soldiers and guns and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was always, always very forbidding and frightening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I made the sign that she should go back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I went down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were about 500.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As it happens-- so it was like that-- on the left hand, let's see-- on the right-hand side-- I still remember it vividly-- there were soldiers with rifles.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "On the left-hand side were Jewish policeman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as it happens, next to me, when I went down-- we were about 500 strong-- there was a Jewish policeman, and his sister was next to me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because we, in this Thebbnz workshop, there were masses of people because they were in an enormous place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he, as we were standing there, just beginning to march, he said, run away, run away, run away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as I heard it, and fearing him--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To his sister.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was standing next to the sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she-- he said it to me, probably, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As, as, as I heard this-- and I was already-- a premonition in my heart was there all the time, the fear.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- without any, you know, thought, I began to run towards this benches-- which I explained to you-- chairs and benches at the end of the place.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this girl, another maybe three, four people, in full speed-- but it was, look, that the soldiers on the other side didn't see us and didn't shoot us outright which they did-- it was a miracle.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we run into this place-- it was quite far-- hid there.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
